snippet.title: Do Not Open | Teaser | #PSTalent2020
snippet.description:
#DoNotOpen is the first video game developed by the studio Quasar Interactive, a spin-off of the company Quasar Dynamics. 

The story revolves around its protagonist, Mike Goreng, who has woken up in a very strange way. He recognizes the place where he is but at the same time he finds it strange, different. 

Only by opening the doors of the house will he discover what has happened and get rid of the threat looms over him. 

You dare to open the door?
